learning_outcomes.en:
- has knowledge of the properties of plastic materials, areas of use, sorting as waste, recycling, reuse; can distinguish different types of plastics;
- is aware of the dangers associated with plastics;
- can process plastic materials manually;
- has general knowledge of the types, properties, areas of use, sorting as waste, recycling, reuse of materials based on wood fiber and wood chemistry;
- can distinguish different materials based on wood fiber and wood composites.

learning_outcomes.et:
- omab teadmisi plastmaterjalide omadustest, kasutusaladest, jäätmena sorteerimisest, ümbertöötlemisest, taaskasutamisest; oskab eristada erinevaid plastiliike markeeringu järgi; 
- on teadlik plastidega kaasnevatest ohtudest; 
- oskab plastmaterjale käsitsi töödelda;
- omab üldteadmisi puidukiul ja puidukeemial põhinevate materjalide liikidest, omadustest, kasutusaladest, jäätmena sorteerimisest, ümbertöötlemisest, taaskasutamisest; 
- oskab eristada erinevaid puidukiul ja puidukeemial põhinevaid materjale.
